      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tricky race. SMALL TOWN HERO (3) broke through for a deserved win here last time as favourite after three runner-up finishes in a row, getting up by a nose in similar company. He maps for every hope up on speed again here and this really shouldn't take any more winning. IMMERSE (5) faded fresh at Caulfield Heath after showing early speed in a tougher affair. She can take plenty from that and do much better here. RING TRUE (1) didn't fire in two Australian runs last time in but is better than that and has been given more time after showing ability in Italy & France before coming. Watch the betting. AXIOM (7) just found one better last time and won't need to improve much at all to be breaking through while BLUE COWBOY (2) can sprint well off a short spell.",
